<idea-plugin version="2" url="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/">
    <name>CSS-X-Fire</name>
    <description><![CDATA[
        <p>Connects Firebug CSS editor with any IDE with CSS capabilities (IntelliJ IDEA Ultimate, PhpStorm, WebStorm, PyCharm, RubyMine).</p>
        <p>Please read the installation guidelines here: <a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/wiki/Installation">http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/wiki/Installation</a></p>
        <p>Style with pleasure!</p>
    ]]></description>
    <version>1.24</version>
    <vendor url="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/" email="ronnie.kolehmainen at gmail.com">Ronnie Kolehmainen</vendor>
    <change-notes><![CDATA[
        <ul>1.24
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=27">Issue 27</a> Support for the !important construct.</li>
            <li>Support for Firefox 9.</li>
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=29">Issue 29</a> Fix for false positives in nested rules.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.23
            <li>Support for Firefox 8.</li>
            <li>
                <a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=4">Issue 4</a> and
                <a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=5">Issue 5</a>
                Initial support for Less and Sass (nested rules).
            </li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.22
            <li>Internal caching of selector and media query searches.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.21
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=23">Issue 23</a> Fixed compability issues with latest EAP's.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.20
            <li>Enabled (automatic) xpi updates from Firefox.</li>
            <li>Support for Firefox 7.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.19
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=22">Issue 22</a> Fixed hotkey error.</li>
            <li>Support custom key binds for all actions.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.18
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=21">Issue 21</a> Reduce filter for currently opened files.</li>
            <li>Support for Firefox 5.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.17
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=18">Issue 18</a> Quick navigation from all nodes with double click or middle mouse click.</li>
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=19">Issue 19</a> Toggle option for automatic expand of changes tree.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.16
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=17">Issue 17</a> Spam protection when using arrow keys in Firebug.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.15
            <li>New settings form.</li>
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=11">Issue 11</a> Configurable route mappings.</li>
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=14">Issue 14</a> Clear pending changes on page leave or refresh (optional settings).</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.14
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=13">Issue 13</a> Made server IP configurable for remote setup (in about:config, filter on cssxfire for options).</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.13
            <li>Also delete trailing semi-colon when removing a declaration.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.12
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=12">Issue 12</a> Compatible with Firefox 4.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.11
            <li>Fixed linking against latest EAPs.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.10
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=8">Issue 8</a> Support for addition of selectors.</li>
            <li>Enqueue incoming changes when in 'dumb' mode (when indices are updated in background).</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.9
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=6">Issue 6</a> Support for CSS media queries.</li>
            <li>Improved selector search/match accuracy.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.8
            <li>Added navigation buttons (prev, next) in toolbar with automatic jump-to-code.</li>
            <li>Toolbar filter(s) group with popup and proper descriptions.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.7
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=7">Issue 7</a> Reduce filter for incoming changes (match specific file only when possible).</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.6
            <li>Fixed updating of UI - keeping tree state and put expand icon on correct nodes.</li>
            <li>Error message and disable tool if local web server cannot be started.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.5
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=2">Issue 2</a> Support for Firebug Lite (Google Chrome and Firefox).</li>
            <li>Changes which are invalid may only be removed.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.4
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=3">Issue 3</a> Trigger automatic upload etc. when applying changes.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.3
            <li><a href="http://code.google.com/p/css-x-fire/issues/detail?id=1">Issue 1</a> Installation help.</li>
            <li>Removed Firefox constraint in internal web server.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.2
            <li>Support for removing properties in Firebug.</li>
            <li>Fixed broken images on help page when not using Firefox.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.1
            <li>Track modifications in source code and invalidate elements in tree view.</li>
            <li>Offer help page dialog on first run or after upgrade.</li>
            <li>Declaration nodes (leafs) are navigatable with double-click or enter key.</li>
            <li>Right-click a node selects it and brings up popup menu.</li>
        </ul>
        <ul>1.0
            <li>Initial version</li>
        </ul>
    ]]>
    </change-notes>
    <idea-version since-build="93.13"/>
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.lang</depends>
    <depends>com.intellij.css</depends>

    <application-components>
        <component>
            <implementation-class>com.googlecode.cssxfire.CssXFireConnector</implementation-class>
        </component>
    </application-components>

    <project-components>
        <component>
            <implementation-class>com.googlecode.cssxfire.IncomingChangesComponent</implementation-class>
        </component>
        <component>
            <implementation-class>com.googlecode.cssxfire.ProjectSettings</implementation-class>
        </component>
        <component>
            <implementation-class>com.googlecode.cssxfire.SearchProcessorCache</implementation-class>
        </component>
    </project-components>

    <actions>

        <action id="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.ApplyAll"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.ApplyAll"
                text="Apply all changes"
                description="Applies all pending changes"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/commit.png"/>
        <action id="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.ClearAll"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.ClearAll"
                text="Clear list"
                description="Clears all pending changes"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/gc.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.DeleteSingle"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.DeleteNode"
                text="Remove selected change"
                description="Removes the selected change from the incoming changelist"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/delete.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.ApplySingle"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.ApplyNode"
                text="Apply selected change"
                description="Applies the selected change from the incoming changelist"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/commit.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.DeleteSelector"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.DeleteNode"
                text="Remove all changes in selector"
                description="Removes all changes from selected CSS selector from the incoming changelist"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/delete.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.ApplySelector"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.ApplyNode"
                text="Apply all changes in selector"
                description="Applies all changes from selected CSS selector from the incoming changelist"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/commit.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.DeleteFile"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.DeleteNode"
                text="Remove all changes in file"
                description="Removes all changes from selected file from the incoming changelist"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/delete.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.ApplyFile"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.ApplyNode"
                text="Apply all changes in file"
                description="Applies all changes from selected file from the incoming changelist"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/commit.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Up"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.Up"
                text="Previous change"
                description="Navigate to the previous occurence"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/up.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Down"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.Down"
                text="Next change"
                description="Navigate to the next occurence"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/down.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Help"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.Help"
                text="Help"
                description="Show the CSS-X-Fire help page"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/help.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.AutoExpand"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.AutoExpand"
                text="Auto Expand"
                description="Expand entire tree on every incoming change."
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/autoexpand.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.ExpandAll"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.ExpandAll"
                text="Expand All"
                description="Expand all elements in the tool window."
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/expandall.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.CollapseAll"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.CollapseAll"
                text="Collapse All"
                description="Collapse all elements in the tool window"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/collapseall.png"/>
        <action id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.ShowSettings"
                class="com.googlecode.cssxfire.action.ShowSettings"
                text="Show Settings"
                description="Edit CSS-X-Fire Settings"
                icon="/com/googlecode/cssxfire/images/applicationSettings.png"/>

        <group id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Single.Invalid" text="" popup="true">
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Delete.Single" ref="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.DeleteSingle"/>
        </group>

        <group id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Single" text="" popup="true">
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Apply.Single" ref="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.ApplySingle"/>
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Delete.Single" ref="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.DeleteSingle"/>
        </group>

        <group id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Selector" text="" popup="true">
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Apply.Selector" ref="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.ApplySelector"/>
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Delete.Selector" ref="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.DeleteSelector"/>
        </group>

        <group id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.File" text="" popup="true">
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Apply.File" ref="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.ApplyFile"/>
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.Delete.File" ref="IncomingChanges.DeclarationNodePopup.DeleteFile"/>
        </group>

        <group id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar" text="" popup="false">
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Button.Help" ref="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Help"/>
            <separator/>
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Button.Up" ref="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Up"/>
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Button.Down" ref="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Down"/>
            <separator/>
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Button.AutoExpand" ref="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.AutoExpand"/>
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Button.ExpandAll" ref="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.ExpandAll"/>
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Button.CollapseAll" ref="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.CollapseAll"/>
            <separator/>
            <reference id="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.Button.ShowSettings" ref="IncomingChanges.ToolBar.ShowSettings"/>
        </group>

    </actions>

    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <projectConfigurable id="com.googlecode.cssxfire.ProjectSettingsConfigurable" implementation="com.googlecode.cssxfire.ProjectSettingsConfigurable"/>
    </extensions>
</idea-plugin>